column1: #FORMAT=WebAnno TSV 3.2
#T_SP=de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.ner.type.NamedEntity|identifier|value
#T_CH=de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.coref.type.CoreferenceLink|referenceRelation|referenceType
#Text=Bolin says : " Follow my lead . "
#Text=Guard post soldier says : " Good afternoon , sir .
#Text=We captured these escaped prisoners .
#Text=We need to get them to a secure facility .
#Text=" Guard post soldier says : " Where did they escape from ?
#Text=" Bolin says : " Camp fourteen .
#Text=" Guard post soldier says : " Then why are you bringing them through here ?
#Text=Camp fourteen is the other way .
#Text=" Bolin says : " You think we do n't know where Camp fourteen is ?
#Text=Kuvira wants them transferred .
#Text=" Guard post soldier says : " Then I 'll need to see the transfer order .
#Text=" Varrick says : " Listen pal !
#Text=I had to fight off two badgermoles , six wolfbats and eighteen hog monkeys to capture these guys , so sorry if I do n't have the paperwork !
#Text=I was too busy cramming it in a hog monkey 's mouth , while it was trying to eat me !
#Text=I am in sore need of a shower and I have blisters that are the size of cantaloupes and twice as juicy !
#Text=So you can let us through , or you can give us your name and rank and I 'll make sure to pass it on to Kuvira !
#Text=You know what happens to soldiers who question her orders , do n't you ?
#Text=Bad stuff !
#Text=" Guard post soldier says : " Let them through !
#Text=" Guard # 2 says : " Wait !
#Text=Stop them , they 're traitors to the Empire !
#Text=" Baraz says : " There 's no way I 'm going back to prison !
#Text=" Varrick says : " Boy , I sure hope this works .
#Text=" Varrick says : " I still got that Varrick touch !
#Text=We 're clear , come on !
#Text=" Bolin says : " Varrick , wait , we ca n't leave them !
#Text=" Guard post soldier says : " Retreat !
#Text=" Baraz says : " Thanks .
#Text=You did n't have to come back .
#Text=" Bolin says : " Yeah .
#Text=I kind of did .
#Text=Let 's go !
#Text="
